{"tid":1637021,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵不歸路上有回程飛？","createTime":"2019-10-08T01:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T01:32:17.000Z","uid":295865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"807239db3ecfeb7de241aa734164fa316b9a7831","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:02:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見好多人講黨鐵有咩惡行，但其實存唔存在黨鐵做返某些野而我地會暫時停止打擊佢地呢？而家明顯佢地配合警慌同正苦做野而搞到大家咁氣憤，但有冇可能我地定左準則，而佢地係跟住做既，我地可以觀察睇睇。始終作為上巿公司雖然係公共業務，插手政治問題已經好唔合邏輯，好明顯就係管理層出左問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正因為咁，其實我地可以集結一D持有黨鐵股票既小股東去信抗議甚至係告佢。主要原因有以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 作為上巿公司應該以商業效慮及大部份股東既利益為依歸，而唔係去插手去處理一D只有政治手段先可以解決既問題<br />\n<br />\n2. 係 2019 年報&quot;致各股東及其他有關人士&quot;裏面講得好清楚 &quot;確定公司在短期內有三件事同樣需要優先處理：&quot;，當中第一點就係 &quot;使公眾對我們建設世界級鐵路的能力恢復信心&quot;，一間已服務為首要重點既上巿公司，7個月內3單撞車事故，睇唔到點樣挽回信心<br />\n<br />\n3. 雖然正苦係黨鐵大股東，但就唔需要效慮其他股東既利益嗎？沒合理狀況下不斷停駛，而停駛中又可以用黎運狗，咁樣果日既生意 (持份者應用既收益）點計呀<br />\n<br />\n4. 而家社會運動持續，而作為商業機構既竟然會插手係處理呢D問題上，明顯就係決策失當，再加上接而連三既事故。真係唔能夠唔同意中科興業在 FB 所講要求更換黨鐵管理層既提議，未能夠帶領公司走向更高既景地，就應該另找有賢者</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人未有持有以上股票，但希望有心人出黎幫幫手"},{"pid":"6fdc207e2d10ed5d3c071737425cf6900f4d776c","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:03:23.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到，如果有人認同既麻煩幫忙推一下"},{"pid":"18471b6475012d5ea7ddecbff9fa2a3b16d9ed45","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:03:40.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"0ee0c158ceb0824da71de258af6290d86da6685c","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:03:50.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"e45caeef6c96a1af906e7ae25659ccf4447920e6","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"a108e4c1cd4d5362adda01e85eee66c74b6b680b","tid":1637021,"uid":295865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:04:13.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"8f033f0f6d80067016b99039924de7f790d4aeb0","tid":1637021,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1732222bfcba1212f4592f4c366cbd27c80fbd2","tid":1637021,"uid":239842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f379837cdc4b2393667a15c56aa7d6ad22a891b9","tid":1637021,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:04:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">又話杯葛？<br />\n又話抗爭？<br />\n繼續俾錢佢賺去出賣港人？<br />\n和理非平時返工唔好再俾正價搭黨鐵！<br />\n無得揀嘅情況例外</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/237n0J0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F237n0J0.jpg&h=61248f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0TeRHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0TeRHg.jpg&h=94f567e9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFtRTVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFtRTVB.jpg&h=5322f0ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxJ20AB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxJ20AB.jpg&h=c7141e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFpQ9Cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFpQ9Cb.jpg&h=a7156522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？"},{"pid":"adb7c8c47a5a95dd9e3164628d57598549626904","tid":1637021,"uid":298066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:08:12.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be00c64b22f9e6d0157dd5eba7606f99189c7748","tid":1637021,"uid":44945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:31:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7be8f98830a76f05473651e2ca6c81fd8ac0ffbc","tid":1637021,"uid":44945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"幫手一推"}]}